      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DR. MONICA (2) had been racing in honest fashion recording two placings in a row before finishing fourth (25.08) at this track latest. Has a good record here at this journey. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings three times from five starts. Tough to beat if on-song. REALITY AWAY (8) looks close to another win after finishing second last time (24.48) in a Bottom Up - Restricted Win at Traralgon. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Expected to be in this for a long way. HURRY DUSTY (4) has mixed form recently, finishing sixth (29.32) in a Mix 6/7 at this track latest but did run well two back when in the frame. This looks easier and expected to improve sharply. BRINDLE MOTION (1) gets a chance to improve on an unplaced run at her latest outing at this circuit. Something for the Multiples: VIENNA ARCHIE (5)",
